  <!-- Comparison Section -->
  <section class="comparison-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">Pilihan Tepat Untuk Bisnismu</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">
      Anda mulai kewalahan memenuhi permintaan pelanggan yang terus meningkat ? dan operasional belum siap mengimbanginya ?
      Mari kita explore perbedaan antara self-fulfillment dan menggunakan layanan Fulfillin, agar anda dapat membuat keputusan yang lebih tepat dan terinformasi.
    </p>

    <div class="comparison-table">
      <!-- POV Column -->
      <div class="comparison-col pov-col">
        <h3>POV (Point of View)</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Focus business strategy</li>
          <li>Operation cost</li>
          <li>System & Technology</li>
          <li>SLA Performance</li>
          <li>Operation Visibility<br>(order, inventory)</li>
          <li>Expand fulfillment<br>to other location</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Fulfillin Column -->
      <div class="comparison-col fulfillin-col">
        <div class="comparison-header">
          <img src="images/logo.webp" alt="fulfillin.id" class="fulfillin-logo">
        </div>
        <ul>
          <li>Client focus for Business strategy development</li>
          <li>Cost Efficiency (Shared multi user facility)</li>
          <li>Support by Fulfillin system (ready to be used)</li>
          <li>Guaranteed by Fulfillin, and possible penalty if out of SLA</li>
          <li>Supported by Fulfillin system</li>
          <li>Possible and ready to be used by Fulfillin multi facility across nationwide</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Individually Column -->
      <div class="comparison-col individually-col">
        <div class="comparison-header">
          <h3>Individually</h3>
        </div>
        <ul>
          <li>Any effort for operation handle (unfocused)</li>
          <li>High Operation cost : Manpower, CAPEX, Opex + Operational issue that possible occurred</li>
          <li>If the client have no system. Any effort, cost, and risk for system development and lack performance</li>
          <li>If any bad performance, the risk absorb 100% by client</li>
          <li>Possible, if the client have own system</li>
          <li>New Effort development & cost</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
